ITEM NO.46               COURT NO.11               SECTION II
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
Petition(s) for Special Leave to Appeal (Crl.)  No(s).  9584/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated  19-06-2025
in CRMWP No. 9232/2025 passed by the High Court of Judicature at
Allahabad]
SATINDER SINGH BHASIN                              Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
STATE OF UTTAR PRADESH & ANR.                      Respondent(s)
(IA No. 152626/2025 - EXEMPTION FROM FILING O.T.)
 
Date : 07-07-2025 This matter was called on for hearing today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE SUDHANSHU DHULIA
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE JOYMALYA BAGCHI
(PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s)  Mr. Sidharth Luthra, Sr. Adv.
                   Mr. Arvind Nayar, Sr. Adv.
                   Ms. Neeha Nagpal, Adv.
                   Mr. Malak Manish Bhatt, AOR
                   Mr. Vishvendra Tomar, Adv.
                   Mr. Praney Sharma, Adv. 
Mr. Vishal Gosain, Adv.
Mr. Malak Bhatt, Adv.                 
                   
For Respondent(s) Mr. S.V.Raju, ASG
Mr. Zoheb Hussain, Adv.
Mr. Annam Venkatesh, Adv.
Mr. Arvind Kumar Sharma, Adv.
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
We have been informed that the matter is pending in the High
Court and the next date in the matter is 09.07.2025.
Let the High Court pass orders on the merit of the case as
presently, we do not see any urgency in the matter. Let the matter
be listed on 21.07.2025 before the appropriate Bench. 
(NIRMALA NEGI)                                  (RENU BALA GAMBHIR)
ASTT. REGISTRAR-cum-PS                        ASSISTANT  REGISTRAR
